                p.conditionsBox__download__app-container--link https://r10.to/hF8RjB

        .conditionsBox__section__method
          .conditionsBox__section__method__wrap
            .conditionsBox__method__title
              p.conditionsBox__method__title__text
                span.method__text__beauty 楽天ビューティ
                | と
